channel.description:
[center][size=15pt]My Hotmail account. sanedevelopment@hotmail.com[/size] Contact me threw MSN to Get the link and discuss further things.
Hey, Hows it going? Yah I know im a first time poster that happenes when you forget your password or a Admin doesnt help you get it back and you have to make a new one. Well.. IF a mod has time please Message me concering how to get my old account "sane" back I would appreciate it. Well anyway I have decided to start a development However this one will actually succeed unlike all the others. Because I already have a .com Domain name and I already have the website and forums created. All Staff for the server and forums will get there own Email such as.. Example@mydomain.com (Cut out domain due to rules) The Server developers will have restricted FTP access to upload there updates.
Ok well heres what I will need for The Server Development
For all these postitions you must add me on MSN and talk to me to get the link then post your proof on MY forums. This is because I am on there more than here and i cant guarantee you ill read it if you post here.
1. Base Server engineer - They will talk to all the Developers and tell me what he thinks should be added I DO NOT HAVE TIME TO DEAL WITH ALL OF THE DEVELOPERS MYSELF (OPEN)
2. Server Coder - They will of course code the server. They need to contact me In MSN to tell me what source we should use. 3 Jobs (OPEN) (OPEN) (OPEN)
3. Forum Moderator - Will monitor the Forums and suggest me with packages for SMF. If you do not know how to do that... Dont bother Applying I added that so I dont get Leechers Signing Up. Rico760 SiForce
4. Client Coders - They will code for the client? (OPEN) (OPEN)
5.Graphic Designer - They will make me any graphics I might request I cant be bothered to make my own im busy. Webbsta (OPEN)
6. Server Hoster Add my MSN to talk more about this. (OPEN)
Im kind of Short Witted here so if you can think of A few more jobs I should add please tell me.
For your sake: Dont bother saying this team sucks and all the negative stuff I could care less what you think. What you think someone else could think of Differently. If your not seriouse About this Dont apply. Because im not taking any stupid crap from anyone.
I am only picking the best of the best so dont apply if your just trieng to do something Im being seriouse about this Team. If you dont have work to show dont bother applying.
You MUST sign up on my forums in order to apply because If you dont it just shows that your not really into this development.\
[code]Runelacose Forum Name: Have you spoken to me on MSN: Why are you good for this JOB: What Job did you apply for: [/code]
[/center]
